        "class": "",
        "text": ",) who did this by her instigation, as this phrase implies; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "had broken up the house of God ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— Had both broken up the treasures, and defaced the house itself. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "And the dedicated things did they bestow upon Baalim — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Gave them, either to adorn the temples of those false gods, or to promote their worship.",
        "children": []
